`gateway-network-link` row of the seedability matrix is partial, so approve the
link by hand:
{% for gw in gateways %}
- **{{ gw.role }} gateway** (`{{ gw.name }}`): {{ gw.url }}
{%- endfor %}

1. Open each **{{ link_source_role }}** gateway, go to Config -> Networking ->
   Gateway Network, and add an outgoing connection to
   `${COMPOSE_PROJECT_NAME}-{{ link_target_service }}` on port 8060.
2. Open the **{{ link_target_role }}** gateway and approve the incoming
   connection request.
